title: Adventures of an Undead Who Became Paladin
alternative_titles: Mai Xiang Ke Li Ma Sha
Adventures of an Undead Who Became Paladin
summary: Adventures of an Undead Who Became Paladin “Humility! Integrity! Compassion! Valor! Justice! Sacrifice! Honor! Faith!” He’s a lich, however, he’s knightly! He is a lich, but he keeps his faith in the light! “Fearless in the face of the enemy! Loyal and upright, he fights to the death! Why you may ask? Because protecting the weak is not against the law of the world!” ……………. This is the story of a cat with a bad mouth and a lich who gave his body and soul to the service of the Light!
